{"tid":885080,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"新居屋彩興苑首10個月錄5撻訂","createTime":"2018-11-01T05:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T15:38:05.000Z","uid":62506,"like":34,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"ec57616a350d1608eff5256a810037ee8b37ab20","tid":885080,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"除了2016年的新居屋現撻訂外，作為出售居者有其屋計劃單位2017的新居屋屋苑近期亦有撻訂個案。<br />\n<br />\n牛頭角彩興苑成交紀錄冊顯示，今年初至今共錄5宗撤銷買賣協議的撻訂個案，其中4宗屬於今年下半年出現，5個單位去年8、9月時售出，成交價261.13萬至360.77萬。<br />\n<br />\n最新一宗撻訂個案為A座1樓6室，面積379平方呎，去年9月以261.13萬元購入，買家於本月初撻訂，若買家為白表客，以最少一成訂金計，估計損失訂金約26.1萬元；若買家為綠表客，以最少5%訂金計，估計損手約13.1萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2197859/%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E5%BD%A9%E8%88%88%E8%8B%91%E9%A6%9610%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%8C%845%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82%20261%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%88%B6%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2197859%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585%25E5%25B1%258B%25E5%25BD%25A9%25E8%2588%2588%25E8%258B%2591%25E9%25A6%259610%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%258C%25845%25E6%2592%25BB%25E8%25A8%2582%2520261%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BD%258E%25E5%25B1%25A4%25E6%2588%25B6%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258F%2596%25E6%25B6%2588%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593&d=AKjg2iWHSuq2wjL7IOPsHdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5a09943f\" target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2197859/%E6%96%B0%E5%B1%85%E5%B1%8B%E5%BD%A9%E8%88%88%E8%8B%91%E9%A6%9610%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%8C%845%E6%92%BB%E8%A8%82%20261%E8%90%AC%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E6%88%B6%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%88%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93</a><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n說好的迫切扵住屋需求呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b75fa2631e12bb86ef93d18e4707bc75d7ad805","tid":885080,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T05:46:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/a